            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">The Enterprise Act 2002, </span><a href="https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2002/40/contents"><span style="color:#0070C0"><u>https://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2002/40/contents</u></span></a></p>
            </content>
          </subparagraph>
